name: Planet Turquoise
description: Planet Turquoise is a purification planet. This planet dispels negative energy and protects against outside influences or pollutants in the atmosphere. Turquoise balances and aligns all the chakras. Here you don’t feel depression and exhaustion, or panic attacks. Here, self-awareness and creative problem solving happen. It is a planet of friendship and romantic love. This planet glows differently under UV light, regular light, and no light.
